## <font color= #00CCFF;font size= 28px;> **管道函数**</font> {data-transition="fade-in slide-out" .bgc data-transition-speed="fast"}  

x %>% f() is equivalent to f(x); x %>% f(y) is equivalent to f(x, y)

<font color= #FF8F56;font size= 28px;>
```{r eval=FALSE}
library(magrittr)

x %>%
  deviation() %>%
  square() %>%
  mean() %>%
  sqrt()
``` 
</font>
